VIEWS SOUGHT ON VISION FOR LOWER RIVER CRANE
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    Residents across the boroughs of Richmond and Hounslow are
    encouraged to have their say on a proposed vision to restore 1.8
    miles of the lower River Crane.

    The Crane Valley Partnership is embarking on the ambitious
    restoration project between the river's divide with the Duke
    of Northumberland and Cole Park Island.

