VIEWS SOUGHT ON PHARMACY SERVICES IN RICHMOND
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    People in Richmond are being asked for their views on the Council's
    draft assessment of the availability of pharmacies and medication
    in the borough.

    These views will inform the Council's final Pharmaceutical Needs
    Assessment (PNA). Findings will be used to advise the NHS on what
    future services need to be provided by NHS pharmacies in Richmond
    upon Thames.

